docs.title: actual notes lol:
docs.text:
getting into this script: (must do this in the right order or vscode won't be able to run it properly)

  • get to documentationTest folder
  • venv\Scripts\activate (this enters (venv) mode)
  • . code to open editor in vscode

mkdocs serve = open live editing of page (local)

mkdocs gh-deploy = publish to github

Will break without telling you if yml file isn't perfectly written, check warnings
